high_descs: Walk forward to the sink, then turn left and walk to the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the tomato in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Walk slightly to the right and face the counter top to the right of the sink.
Put the tomato on the counter, behind and to the left of the other tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned tomato on a counter top.

high_descs: walk to face counter to the right of stove
pick up tomato from counter top
wash tomato in sink, pick up tomato from sink
walk slightly right to face counter to the right of sink
put tomato on counter to the left of tomato already there
anns.task_desc: put a washed tomato onto a counter top

high_descs: Walk to the sink, turn left, and walk to the counter beside the stove.
Pick up the tomato behind the green goblet.
Turn completely around and walk halfway back across the room, turn left so you are facing the sink.
Place the tomato in the left side of the sink, run water into both sides, drain and pick up the tomato again.
Turn right, walk to the microwave, turn left and face the counter next to the sink.
Place the tomato on the counter next to the other tomato.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the tomato beside the stove and put with the other tomato on the counter.
